query:
DELETE FROM peers
                    WHERE (user_id, torrent_id, peer_id) IN (
                        SELECT t.user_id, t.torrent_id, t.peer_id
                        FROM (
                            SELECT * FROM unnest(
                                $1::int[],
                                $2::int[],
                                $3::bytea[]
                            ) AS t(user_id, torrent_id, peer_id)
                        ) AS t
                    )
